reater}M{\textless}i/{\textgreater}{\textless}sub{\textgreater}{\textless}i{\textgreater}*{\textless}i/{\textgreater}{\textless}sub/{\textgreater} is not solely driven by gas accretion. The results presented in this paper emphasize the need to invoke a more complex mix of physical processes including major and minor merging to further understand the co-evolution of the SFR and stellar mass growth.},
