	abstract = {We have updated the Munich galaxy formation model, L-GALAXIES, to follow 
the radial distributions of stars and atomic and molecular gas in galaxy
discs. We include an H2-based star-formation law, as well as
a detailed chemical-enrichment model with explicit mass-dependent delay
